library(readxl)
li_feng_SQ_neg <- read_xlsx('./metabolism.cell/许丽霞-BQ-XLX20220105-QE-SQ-项目交付.lipid/许丽霞 BQ-XLX20220105-QE-SQ-分析报告/Analysis result/report/results/NEG/Statistical Analysis/NEG-ori.xlsx') 
li_feng_SQ_pos <- read_xlsx('./metabolism.cell/许丽霞-BQ-XLX20220105-QE-SQ-项目交付.lipid/许丽霞 BQ-XLX20220105-QE-SQ-分析报告/Analysis result/report/results/POS/Statistical Analysis/POS-ori.xlsx') 
li_feng_SQ_neg <- li_feng_SQ_neg %>% 
  dplyr::mutate(MS_name=coalesce(MS2.name,MS1.name)) %>%
  relocate(MS_name,.before = MS1.name) %>% 
  distinct(`MS_name`,.keep_all = T)  %>%
  dplyr::filter(!is.na(MS_name),) %>% 
  column_to_rownames('MS_name') %>% dplyr::select(matches("CT1")) %>% 
  rownames_to_column('MS_name')
li_feng_SQ_pos <- li_feng_SQ_pos %>% 
    dplyr::mutate(MS_name=coalesce(MS2.name,MS1.name)) %>%
    relocate(MS_name,.before = MS1.name) %>% 
    distinct(`MS_name`,.keep_all = T)  %>%
    dplyr::filter(!is.na(MS_name),) %>% 
  column_to_rownames('MS_name') %>% dplyr::select(matches("CT1"))%>% 
  rownames_to_column('MS_name')

colnames(li_feng_SQ_neg) <- str_remove(colnames(li_feng_SQ_neg),"_neg")
colnames(li_feng_SQ_pos) <- str_remove(colnames(li_feng_SQ_pos),"_pos")
li_feng_SQ <- rbind(li_feng_SQ_neg,li_feng_SQ_pos) %>% 
  distinct(MS_name,.keep_all = T)
li_feng_SQ <- li_feng_SQ %>% column_to_rownames('MS_name')

数据宽表转长表

li_feng_SQ <-li_feng_SQ %>% 
  rownames_to_column('meta') %>% 
  relocate(meta,.before = everything()) %>% 
  pivot_longer(colnames(.)[-1],names_to = 'sample',values_to = 'vol') %>% 
  dplyr::mutate(group=ifelse(str_detect(sample,"_E"),"ESP","Ctrl"))

筛选Fold和p值满足条件代谢物

li_feng_SQ_p <-li_feng_SQ %>%  dplyr::select(-sample) %>% group_by(meta) %>% 
  summarise(pvalue=t.test(vol[group=='ESP'],vol[group=='Ctrl'])$p.value,
            fold=mean(vol[group=='ESP'])/mean(vol[group=='Ctrl'])) %>% 
  dplyr::filter(pvalue<0.05) %>% dplyr::filter(fold>=1)

li_feng_SQ_p2 <-li_feng_SQ_p %>% dplyr::filter(str_detect(meta,'Cer|FA|TAG|CE|CL|PC|PE|PL|Pl|DAG|SM'))
li_feng_SQ_p2 <-li_feng_SQ_p2 %>% dplyr::arrange(desc(fold))

绘制代谢物热图（每个样本的情况）

li_feng_SQ2 <- li_feng_SQ2[rownames(li_feng_SQ2) %in% li_feng_SQ_p2$meta,]
pheatmap::pheatmap(li_feng_SQ2 ,scale = 'row',cluster_rows = T,cluster_cols = F)

library(jjAnno)
library(ggplotify)
plot <- scale(t(li_feng_SQ2)) %>% t() %>% as.data.frame()
plot <- plot %>% 
  rownames_to_column('meta') %>% 
  relocate(meta,.before = everything()) %>% 
  pivot_longer(colnames(.)[-1],names_to = 'sample',values_to = 'vol')
plot$group <- case_when(str_detect(plot$meta,"FA")~"Fatty acid",
                        str_detect(plot$meta,"TAG")~"triacylglycerol",
                        str_detect(plot$meta,"PC")~"Phosphatidylcholine",
                        str_detect(plot$meta,"PE")~"Phosphatidylethanolamine",
                        str_detect(plot$meta,"Cer")~"ceramides")
plot <- left_join(plot,li_feng_SQ_p2,by='meta')
plot <- plot %>% dplyr::arrange(desc(group),desc(fold))
plot$meta <- factor(plot$meta,levels = unique(plot$meta))
plot$group <- factor(plot$group,levels = unique(plot$group))
p2 <- ggplot(data = plot,aes(x=sample,y=meta))+
  geom_tile(aes(fill = vol),colour = "white")+
  scale_fill_gradient2(low='#4475b4',mid = '#fefdc0',high='#d73027')+
  theme_bw()+
  theme(
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    panel.border = element_blank(),
    axis.title = element_blank(),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90))+coord_cartesian(clip = 'off')+ theme(plot.margin=unit(rep(3,4),'cm'))
p2

p3 <- annoRect(p2,annoPos = 'left',aesGroup = T,aesGroName = 'group',xPosition = c(-9,0.3),
         addText = T,textCol = rep('black',5),textHVjust = -7,alpha = 0.4,
         rectWidth = 0.8,textSize = 5.5,fontface = 'bold',vjust = 4)
